OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779444433
OL,3,CMan died after tree fell on caravan
OL,4,Cduring Storm Goretti, inquest hears
OL,6,FA 50-year-old gardener was killed when
OL,7,Fa large tree uprooted and fell on to
OL,8,Fhis static caravan during Storm
OL,9,FGoretti, an inquest hears.
OL,11,FFather of two, James Southey was found
OL,12,Fdead on Friday 9 January in the
OL,13,Fcaravan which he rented on a farm at
OL,14,FParc an Fold farm at Mawgan near
OL,15,FHelston, Cornwall.
OL,17,FHe had lived there for around a decade
OL,18,Fand was 'happy' there and he got on
OL,19,Fwell with the landowners and
OL,20,Fneighbours.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
