PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779444433
OL,3,CMan died after tree fell on caravan
OL,4,Cduring Storm Goretti, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe caravan was sited between two
OL,7,Flarge trees - in one James had built a
OL,8,Ftree house for his sons - and the
OL,9,Ftrees had been checked in the summer
OL,10,Fof 2025 and no maintenance was needed.
OL,12,FA severe red weather warning of risk
OL,13,Fto life was in place for high winds in
OL,14,Fthe area that evening.
OL,16,FAn inquest heard today that the tree
OL,17,Fcrashed down on to the living area of
OL,18,Fthe caravan and landed on James
OL,19,FSouthey who died from suffocation
OL,20,Fcaused by the weight of the tree trunk
OL,21,Fon his chest.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779444433
OL,3,CMan died after tree fell on caravan
OL,4,Cduring Storm Goretti, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe had not consumed any alcohol but
OL,7,Fthere was recent use of cannabis, said
OL,8,Fa toxicoloy report.
OL,10,FFarmer Martin Williams said he looked
OL,11,Fout from his home and saw James
OL,12,Fcooking and a light from his log
OL,13,Fburner - but then there was a power
OL,14,Fcut.
OL,16,FMartin recounted how he looked towards
OL,17,Fthe caravan and could not see the log
OL,18,Fburner and they raced to the scene but
OL,19,Fcould not access it because of the
OL,20,Fsize of the uprooted tree.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779444433
OL,3,CMan died after tree fell on caravan
OL,4,Cduring Storm Goretti, inquest hears
OL,6,FMartin cut his hand smashing a window
OL,7,Fbut he was unable to get to the living
OL,8,Farea which had been crumpled by the
OL,9,Ffallen tree.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called and
OL,12,Farrived at the scene an hour later due
OL,13,Fto problems caused by the storm.
OL,15,FMartin said: "The police arrived and
OL,16,Fsaid there was nothing they could do
OL,17,Fduring the storm to access where James
OL,18,Fwas."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
