OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779444433
OL,3,CMan died after tree fell on caravan
OL,4,Cduring Storm Goretti, inquest hears
OL,6,FPolice guarded the area overnight and
OL,7,Fcrews retrieved his body the next day
OL,8,Fafter cutting away three large tree
OL,9,Flimbs and part of the roof.
OL,11,FAn arborist said the tree and its
OL,12,Fcanopy were healthy but it was not a
OL,13,Fnative tree and its roots were shallow
OL,14,Fand there was a lot of water in the
OL,15,Farea and the ground was sodden.
OL,17,FDet Con Kirsty McNeill said winds of
OL,18,F90mph were around that area that night
OL,19,Fas Storm Goretti hit Cornwall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
