PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779444433
OL,3,CMan died after tree fell on caravan
OL,4,Cduring Storm Goretti, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said emergency crews could not do
OL,7,Fmore during the storm as there was a
OL,8,Frisk to their safety from live
OL,9,Felectrics, gas canisters and other
OL,10,Ftrees.
OL,12,FCoroner Miss Hillson recorded an
OL,13,Faccidental death conclusion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
